<author>Saihnuna</author>
<title>Ei Nungsawn Ki'n</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van khawpi tuollai a leng sa,
 Lei lungkham thuok in Amau hi;
 &quot;Hepa, ei nungsawn kiin&quot; A tii.
 Panpih A ngai ie, A sakmel ka thil in.

[V2]
 Lal mel ka muh tieng pakin la sangka,
 Khawvel dahum hi kei di'n nunnawpna hung hina;
 Van ka nawplenna ding gam chu,
 Ni cheng in thil ka.

[V3]
 2. Israel nam suihlung mawl chu,
 Salem kulh sung dogal in chang;
 Lal thisan namtin din a luong,
 Ka gitloh nen teutui bang thien nang ahi.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa tatna thisan luong,
 Kalvari hansie dawl tuolthing;
 Bela linglukhuk A khuk lai,
 Muh ka nuom na e, aw van khawpi thak tawh.</lyrics>
</song>